Class TransitionSet

java.lang.Object
  org.springframework.webflow.engine.TransitionSet

public class TransitionSet
extends java.lang.Object

A typed set of transitions for use internally by artifacts that can apply transition execution logic.

Author:
Keith Donald
See Also:
